title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jun 13 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jun 13 2022
description:
10 Republican senators join Democrats on gun control bill. Justin Trudeau: There's no right to self defense in Canada. Journo Taylor Lorenz's crazy tweet on covid precautions. Rep. Elise Stefanik joins Clay and Buck to discuss Democrat efforts to pass gun control and the Jan. 6 show trial. Bill Maher hits NYT for burying Kavanaugh assassination attempt. Obama advisor Steve Rattner echoes C&B: Manchin saved Democrats.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
